title: Haven't received an arcade icon
body: After completing the quest Villains rule! I didn't got an icon despite that I fulfilled the quest and it's now in my completed ones, but I haven't received the arcade icon. Please fix this.  I can't find it anywhere... http://prikachi.com/images.php?images/588/9160588H.png

replies.body: Some of those delivery poros must have gotten a little lazy, but no worries! I've got my best poros on the job! You should be seeing that icon show up shortly.
